OL,3,CNew National Park proposed in Galloway
OL,5,FGalloway has been selected as the
OL,6,Flocation for Scotland's next National
OL,7,FPark.
OL,9,FLocal residents, communities and
OL,10,Fbusinesses will now be invited to
OL,11,Fshare their views on whether Galloway
OL,12,Fshould become a new National Park and
OL,13,Fwhere the boundary for the new park
OL,14,Fshould be drawn.
OL,16,FRob Lucas, Chair of Galloway National
OL,17,FPark Association said: "This is
OL,18,Ffantastic news that the case for
OL,19,FGalloway to be proposed as Scotland's
OL,20,Fthird National Park has been
OL,21,Frecognised.
