OL,3,CNew National Park proposed in Galloway
OL,5,F"It would bring transformational
OL,6,Feconomic and environmental benefits to
OL,7,Fthe area and strengthen our local
OL,8,Fcommunities."
OL,10,FDuring a visit to Galloway, Rural
OL,11,FAffairs Secretary Mairi Gougeon said:
OL,12,F"After carefully considering all of
OL,13,Fthe nominations we received, I am very
OL,14,Fpleased that we are proposing to
OL,15,Fcreate a new National Park for
OL,16,FScotland in Galloway.
