OL,3,CNew National Park proposed in Galloway
OL,5,F"The proposal is community led, has
OL,6,Fthe backing of many local businesses
OL,7,Fand makes a strong case on the
OL,8,Fbenefits that National Park status
OL,9,Fwill bring for people who live in the
OL,10,Farea, for the local economy and for
OL,11,Fthe environment.
OL,13,F"We received nominations for new
OL,14,FNational Parks from some really
OL,15,Fspecial places ` Lochaber, Loch Awe,
OL,16,FScottish Borders and Tay Forest.
