OL,3,CNew National Park proposed in Galloway
OL,5,FScotland currently has two National
OL,6,FParks, but it's been more than two
OL,7,Fdecades since a new one was
OL,8,Festabilished.
OL,10,FIn 2021 the SNP and Scottish Greens
OL,11,Fagreed to create "at least one" more
OL,12,FNational Park to join the Cairngorms
OL,13,Fand Loch Lomond and the Trossachs.
OL,15,FDespite the collapse of the power-
OL,16,Fsharing deal between the two parties
OL,17,Fearlier this year, the Scottish
OL,18,FGovernment confirmed it would contiune
OL,19,Fits commitment to create at least one
OL,20,Fnew National Park by 2026.
