OL,3,CNew National Park proposed in Galloway
OL,5,FWhat happens next?
OL,7,FThe next stage will include a
OL,8,Fconsultation and investigation by
OL,9,FNatureScot into the proposed location
OL,10,Fwhich it will submit to Ministers in
OL,11,FApril next year.
OL,13,FThe consultation will look at the
OL,14,Fproposed boundaries as well as support
OL,15,Ffrom local people, communities and
OL,16,Fbusinesses.
OL,18,FIt should also take account of local
OL,19,Fcircumstances and help to meet the
OL,20,Fneeds of communities.
