OL,3,CNew National Park proposed in Galloway
OL,5,FNatureScot Chair Professor Colin
OL,6,FGalbraith said: "NatureScot welcomes
OL,7,Fthe Cabinet Secretary for Rural
OL,8,FAffairs' commission to investigate the
OL,9,Fproposed location of Galloway for
OL,10,FScotland's next National Park.
OL,12,F"We are looking forward to the
OL,13,Fextensive opportunity for
OL,14,Fconsultation, building on our
OL,15,Fexperience with Scotland's first two
OL,16,FNational Parks.
OL,18,F"In preparing our advice, we will
OL,19,Fconsult widely with everyone who has
OL,20,Fan interest in this special place.
